{"tid":1567333,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「唱歌遊行2.0」 文宣也瘋狂，全面進化！","createTime":"2019-09-14T04:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:16:58.000Z","uid":184099,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"c880bd48ff4f0bd597b466ce06a57ea2e7b8dd48","tid":1567333,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"係時候要進化啦各位！之前開post無乜人睇到<br />\n每次遊行唱歌集會print文宣，A4 size都得！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「唱歌2.0」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n帶備黏貼材料（膠紙/白膠漿），<br />\n文宣材料（down落黎print，對準政權之宣傳），<br />\n唱完歌仔之後，<br />\n一齊去附近連儂場度貼滿佢！<br />\n去到邊貼到邊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「遊行2.0」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「連儂場2.0」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n鑑於最近藍隊升級進化，連儂場被清得快。<br />\n小弟分析後，原因是因為「連儂場過於集中同一地點」！<br />\n<br />\n解決辦法：<br />\n唱歌之後有大量人手貼。「遊行之後可以貼馬路（平日難清理）」<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n香城online開服已經3個月，要全面進化！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想象下，200萬人出黎遊行，1人貼10張，條街有2000萬張文宣。我屌？屈唔屈機？屌？？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n推我上熱門，全世界全面升級！"},{"pid":"32f10d5c34efa868b73cd6c3b3f7942cccc24088","tid":1567333,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"915 928 帶文宣出黎齊齊貼！"},{"pid":"7075f5b34a63bf0eceb148f4407d8eace61a4568","tid":1567333,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"915 928 帶文宣出黎齊齊貼！"},{"pid":"43eb386091f79a18315ffbce1320f1a7d7945352","tid":1567333,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"915 928 帶文宣出黎齊齊貼！"},{"pid":"94352698b2811260f7569f6b57a89a4853c24720","tid":1567333,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"915 928 帶文宣出黎齊齊貼！"},{"pid":"3cf36f17235b2f2fae5fe321e66faa